---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now"
  description="What Matteo Antonini is working on right now."
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-12" transition:animate="fade">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Now</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Last updated: June 2026</p>
    </header>

    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none" transition:animate="fade">
      <h2>Work</h2>
      <p>
        Working as an AI Engineer. Day-to-day focus is on agentic
        AI and multi-agent system design for clients in energy, telco, and public administration.
      </p>

      <h2>Side projects</h2>
      <p>
        Building personal and business automations using n8n and Apify — mostly tools that
        eliminate repetitive workflows: scraping, data processing, notifications, integrations.
        Lots of trial and error, which is the point.
      </p>

      <h2>Teaching</h2>
      <p>
        Running the multi-agent systems module for the <a href="/teaching">Master CESMA</a> at
        the University of Rome Tor Vergata, 2026 edition.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
